The property boasts panoramic views that stretch from Newport Beach to DTLA, and the standout feature is the extensive private rooftop deck that spans over 2500 sq.ft. The penthouse itself is over 2400 sq.ft and showcases 18-foot-high domed ceilings that exude elegance. It is the only unit in the building to have its own laundry hookups. This unique property is located in the East Village Arts District of Downtown Long Beach and is recognized as a historic landmark. It was originally built as a supper club and event space for the city's rich and famous. The penthouse is perfect for entertaining guests and hosting events like the most recent art event featured in the property photos showcasing local artisans. The property also includes a grand lobby with on-site management, on-site laundry, a fully equipped game room, a BBQ and garden area, and an expansive gym - Long Beach's largest private complex gym.

The Willmore building, an architectural marvel, proudly showcases the grandeur of European Renaissance architectural designs. This condominium caters to discerning individuals, whether young professionals seeking a chic urban sanctuary, artists inspired by the industrial loft ambiance, or investors in search of a prime downtown Long Beach property.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary condominium your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience luxury urban living at its finest in downtown Long Beach!

Welcome to 3455 Rose Avenue, Long Beach in the charming Long Beach neighborhood of California Heights. When you enter into California Heights, you'll immediately notice that you are in a neighborhood that has pride of ownership of its charming residences. Yet when you pull up to this home, you will without a doubt know that this is one of the prettiest homes on the block. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single family residence is freshly remodeled for its future owners. From the minute you walk in on the luxury vinyl plank flooring you will love the open concept this house reaps. From the vintage French doors to the large bay window that looks out to the front yard, to the beautiful finishes, this home has it all! The kitchen is beautifully remodeled with soft close white shaker cabinets and drawers. The counters are gorgeous luxury quartz, and the appliances are all stainless steel. From the freshly painted walls to the brand-new baseboards to the brand-new windows, to the LED lights, this home has no stone left unturned. The master suite is the real head turner! This incredibly large suite has room for any size bed and tons of furniture. When you walk through what could very well be your future bedroom, imagine how you would decorate and design this space that has plenty of options. The walk-in closet is massive and has plenty of space for all the clothes you could imagine. The master bathroom has been recently modeled with brand new tile flooring, a gorgeous vanity, and beautiful tile walls for your shower/tub. This home has a great sized detached two-car garage with alley way access. It also has a gate where you could easily move a boat or jet skis to your back concrete storage area. And yes, the storage containers AND jacuzzi comes with the home. The backyard is a great space to have some quiet time. You have your grass area for your kiddos to play in, a beautiful avocado tree, and even a back patio for any entertaining that you might do. We can't wait for you to take a look at what could be your future home at 3455 Rose Avenue.

Nestled in the sought-after neighborhood of California Heights in Long Beach, California, this fully remodeled Spanish-style home seamlessly blends classic charm with modern comforts. Outside, the backyard is a private sanctuary with space for outdoor dining and relaxation. Located in California Heights, this property offers the perfect blend of historic charm and modern living. Nearby amenities include local shops, restaurants, and parks, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a vibrant community atmosphere.    In summary, this fully remodeled Spanish-style home in Long Beach's California Heights neighborhood offers a harmonious fusion of classic architecture, contemporary comforts, and a prime location, making it an exceptional place to call home.

column79: Location, lifestyle, with Omni Resort golf course views. Top model tankless water heater for unlimited hot water allowing usage of all 3 showers simultaneously if needed. High ceiling in living room with built-in surround sound ceiling speakers. Alarm system with motion detectors. 50ft of multiple balconies with golf views. Garage has waterspout with plenty of driveway space to wash personal items. Quaint little backyard on par 5 of La Costa Golf Course with Japanese garden inspired seating area. Corner end unit sharing only one common wall and nestled off the street on a cul-de-sac. Very private with significant distance from other homes on front entry side and golf course side. Only 5 homes share this development. Any or all furniture can be negotiated into price.

For nearly 30 years the family of this gorgeous home has lived in this quiet neighborhood and raised their beautiful family. Now they are looking for the next family to do the same.  Rancho Ponderosa is conveniently located on the border of La Costa and Encinitas and is located just a few miles from some of southern California's most famous beaches. You and your family will enjoy being centrally located near local shopping malls, restaurant's and award winning schools. The community boasts low HOA fees and a low tax base. Now let's talk about this perfect 4 bedroom 3 bath home with a bonus craft room that can be a 5th bedroom or office. The seller has spent $$$ over the years keeping this place in tip top shape. Downstairs boasts a formal living room, dining room, a gourmet Kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and beautiful 20 x 20 ceramic tile floors. The kitchen overlooks the family room that spills out into your dream backyard. Like to entertain?  That's exactly what this backyard was designed for. Your new dream backyard is nearly all low maintenance concrete with a aluma-wood patio cover, custom island with a sink and fridge, and of course a sparkling pool (recently re-plastered) and spa you can enjoy almost year round with due to Carlsbad's nearly perfect weather. Downstairs also has one bedroom and full bath for guests. Upstairs the large master bedroom has a double door entry and a completely remodeled bathroom with granite countertops and a walk in shower. Shopping, Services & Entertainment are just a few minutes away, as is Yorba Linda Regional Park, Placentia Yorba Linda School District, Hiking, Biking, Swan Pedal Boats, 11 Miles away from Disneyland and much, much more. There's also easy access to 91, 55, 57, & 241 Freeways. Space Rent is only $1,531.00

Experience the best of Anaheim Hills living on a quiet cul-de-sac where pride of ownership abounds!  This single level residence boasts four bedrooms, two bathrooms and 1,936 square feet of grand living area on a sizeable 7,200 square foot lot. Formal living and dining room with cozy fireplace, alongside bright kitchen that opens to family room and breakfast nook. Large primary suite with ensuite bath and dual closets. Enjoy the spacious 3-car garage and gated RV or boat parking. The home is finished with automatic sprinklers, a lush front courtyard, and backyard firepit. Easy access awaits-walk to school, dining, park or bike trail, and drive only three minutes to the 91 and 55 freeways.  Fifteen minutes to Disneyland and 20 minutes to the beach!  Base property taxes, no Mello Roos and no HOA. A perfect place to make your own!

SINGLE LEVEL RANCH STYLE HOME * GUEST HOME * EXTRA WIDE LOT * RV/BOAT PARKING * COVERED WORK SHED * REMODELLED KITCHEN * PARKING FOR UP TO 10 CARS!...This stunning single-level ranch-style property, spanning 2,494 sq. ft., with an additional 630 sq. ft. one bedroom, one bathroom guest house, for a combined 3124 sq. ft. of living space offers modern elegance with practical amenities, all nestled on an exceptionally large lot.  The main house features 4 generous bedrooms and 3 tastefully designed bathrooms. The vaulted, beamed ceilings create an open and airy ambiance, complemented by a blend of luxury vinyl plank flooring and plush carpeting for a seamless flow throughout. The fully remodeled kitchen is a culinary delight, featuring newer stainless steel appliances including a refrigerator, dishwasher, multi-burner gas cooktop, oven, microwave, and a farm-style single basin sink. Large picturesque windows in the living areas showcase stunning views of the backyard oasis, bringing in natural light and enhancing the home's open feel. Step outside to a beautifully landscaped backyard with a sparkling pool, rock water feature, and gas firepit. A covered patio provides the perfect spot for relaxing in the shade, while an outdoor half bathroom adds convenience for poolside guests. The guest house is a private retreat, featuring a spacious living area complete with a sink and refrigerator, a standalone bedroom offering privacy and comfort, and a large bathroom with a walk-in shower, ensuring a luxurious experience for guests. The lot is nearly double the size of neighboring properties, offering unparalleled space and flexibility. In addition to a two-car garage, the property includes a covered carport and a spacious covered workshop with a car lift, ideal for enthusiasts or additional RV/boat storage. The workshop also features a 50 amp outlet for extra power needs, and there is plenty of additional parking space next to the workshop. The home also boasts a durable cement roof, an open floor plan designed for easy living and entertaining with plenty of natural light, and an elegant wood-finished bar that adds a touch of sophistication to the living space. This property is the epitome of luxury and practicality, offering everything you need for comfortable living and entertainment. Whether you're hosting family and friends, working on projects, or simply enjoying the serene environment. Don't miss the opportunity to own this extraordinary property!

Welcome to this beautiful mid-century modern home nestled on a peaceful corner lot, perfectly positioned between the coveted neighborhoods of Yorba Linda and Anaheim Hills. Located within the esteemed Placentia Yorba Linda School District and within walking distance to Esperanza High and Glenview Elementary schools, this home offers both convenience and top-rated education options for families. Step inside through the new entry door into an inviting space featuring high vaulted ceilings, seamlessly blending the formal living and dining rooms adorned with a cozy fireplace. The home boasts a total of 4 bedrooms and 2 beautifully remodeled bathrooms, including a luxurious primary ensuite with a glass walk-in shower. The heart of this home is the stunning newly remodeled kitchen, complete with quartz countertops, rich brown cabinetry with soft-close drawers, stainless steel appliances, a built in wine rack and an expansive island. Adjacent to the kitchen is ample space for a breakfast nook, overlooking the backyard retreat. Entertain effortlessly with a layout that flows from indoor to outdoor living, highlighted by a spacious back patio with an Aluma wood patio cover, perfect for enjoying Southern California's weather year-round. The low-maintenance landscaping and pavered backyard ensure easy upkeep and leisurely weekends. Additional features include indoor laundry facilities, new flooring throughout, newer dual pane windows, fresh paint inside and out, and a soft water unit. This home has been meticulously maintained and updated to offer modern comforts while preserving its mid-century charm. With a 2-car garage and driveway, there's ample parking and storage space. The property is fully fenced for privacy and security, providing a serene oasis in a desirable neighborhood. Don't miss your chance to own this immaculate and beautifully upgraded mid-century modern home that seamlessly combines comfort, style, and functionality. Schedule a tour today and envision yourself living in this entertainer's dream home in one of Orange County's most sought-after locations.

Welcome to this exquisite dream home nestled in the tranquil hills of Brea, where sophistication and comfort harmonize at every turn. This captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence spans 2336 square feet of sheer elegance.    Upon entering from the charming porch, you're welcomed by soaring ceilings that enhance the spacious living and dining areas. The large formal area provides an elegant yet warm environment,  ideal for hosting gatherings. The beautifully remodeled kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting pristine white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and an open layout seamlessly connecting to the breakfast area and inviting family room, complete with a custom-built entertainment center.    The downstairs bedroom, currently used as an office, offers versatility and convenience. Upstairs, the spacious primary suite awaits, providing a luxurious retreat with a walk-in closet, separate walk-in shower, soaking tub, and dual sinks, offering a sanctuary for relaxation. Two additional bedrooms are connected by a stylish Jack and Jill bathroom, ensuring comfort and privacy for family or guests.    The 3 car garage is a well-appointed multipurpose space, featuring tile floor, finished walls and ceiling with recessed lighting and ample white cabinetry, creating an organized and polished area for storage, projects, or entertainment.    Outside, the backyard paradise beckons, boasting a private pool and spa, perfect for refreshing dips on hot summer days, while the expansive patio invites al fresco dining and entertaining under the stars. Direct access to the downstairs bath and shower from the pool adds to the convenience. Gas, water and electric is ready for your outdoor kitchen!    Situated on a tranquil street with no through traffic in one of Brea's premier neighborhoods, this immaculate home epitomizes peaceful suburban living. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shopping, restaurants, entertainment, schools, and freeways, all while residing in a wonderful neighborhood that exudes charm and community spirit.    Don't miss out on this gem of a property. Schedule your showing today and make this luxurious retreat yours before it's gone.

THIS HOME IS A MUST SEE!  Prepare to fall in love with this pristine "Forever Home", the definition of pride in ownership, updated and improved, located on a quiet Cul-De-Sac nestled up to a greenbelt in the highly desired Country Hills Estates.    It features a bright and open floor plan with 4 bedrooms (4th bedroom used as upstairs bonus room), 2.5 bathrooms with approximately 2,606 square feet of spacious living space AND is walking distance to Country Hills Elementary.  Completely remodeled kitchen with professional grade stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, massive center island and French doors leading to backyard. The landscaped backyard is anchored by four palm trees which overlook a salt water pool & spa, covered gazebo, fire-pit and raised patio which will give your family years of memories. Upstairs you will find the extra large master bedroom with adjacent master bathroom with dual vanities, custom paint and dual closets. The oversized bonus room features vaulted ceilings, custom built-ins and plenty of natural light. Downstairs laundry room and two car attached garage with custom built-ins has plenty of room for storage. Close to Downtown Brea, Downtown Fullerton, Movies, Improv, Fabulous Restaurants, Nightlife and Award Winning Schools. Low low HOA and no mello roos.

Beautiful SINGLE-STORY home located in the highly sought-after community of North Hills! This home features a bright and open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with 2,000 square feet of spacious living space. You are welcomed at the entry into the living room that features soaring cathedral ceilings, beautiful brick fireplace with mantle, large window for natural lighting and is adjacent to the formal dining room. The spacious kitchen features white shaker cabinets with soft close hinges, granite countertops, double oven, gas cooktop with stainless steel microwave overhead, large peninsula with counter bar seating that overlooks the family room and breakfast nook. LARGE Owner suite features large bedroom area with vaulted ceiling and direct access to the patio, mirrored closets, beautiful vanity area and walk in shower. Three additional spacious bedrooms and a beautiful full bath down the hall. Backyard has been renovated with new drip irrigation and drainage system, beautiful rose garden, lemon trees, gas line to connect your BBQ and LED landscape lighting system. Additional features of the home include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, double pane windows, interior laundry, and 2-car garage with BRAND NEW smart Wi-Fi enabled garage door opener. Take advantage of the Low HOA that includes newly renovated pool, clubhouse, tot lot, Pickle Ball Court, Tennis Courts and greenbelt walkway. Located in the Award-winning Brea Olinda Unified School District, Close to the Brea Mall, Downtown Brea, shopping and restaurants. Come view this beautiful house and make it yours today!

FULLY REMODELED 2 STORY IN THE HEART OF COUNTRY HILLS WITH A VIEW! Fully upgraded 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, 2,043 Sq.Ft. home in the highly sought-after community of Country Hills in Brea! This home features brand new LVT flooring, fresh interior and exterior paint, recessed lighting and upgrades throughout. A large double-door entry leads you into the foyer, where you will immediately notice the open floor plan concept. To the left is the sunken formal living room with a gorgeous quartz fireplace, vaulted ceilings, and plenty of windows for natural lighting. The remodeled kitchen sparkles with quartz countertops, new soft-close cabinets, a farmhouse sink, bar seating, and new stainless-steel appliances. Adjacent, is an additional dining room as well as the family room with large windows and direct access to the backyard. Upstairs are 5 bedrooms with new carpet for comfort including the spacious primary suite which includes large windows and a remodeled ensuite bathroom with a dual sink quartz vanity, walk-in shower, and a large walk-in closet. Down the hall are the 4 secondary bedrooms and a fully upgraded bathroom, including a vanity with quartz counters and a shower-tub combo. A beautiful open backyard with panoramic skyline and Disneyland fireworks views is the perfect spot for entertaining. Additional highlights include an upgraded half bathroom downstairs for guests, custom finishes and fixtures throughout, and a two-car garage with a wide driveway that could fit an RV. The Country Hills Community is extremely walkable with multiple community green belts, and just a short walk to Country Hills Elementary School & Park. Situated just a few minutes from Birch Hills Golf Course, Brea Mall, Downtown Brea, with freeway access nearby - this home is one you won't want to miss out on!

Lake Park Brea** Rare 2 bedroom home in great condition - Original Owner has maintained this home from the beginning - Low Space rent for New Owner will be just $1336.37!  It's one of the largest homes in the Park - It has a secluded/private very large concrete patio area which is covered for shade, and a fully walled and gated yard - Plenty of room for a garden or to watch the Grandchildren or your pets play safely.  No lawn maintenance as it's quality artificial "grass" - Front porch has enough room for a small table and a couple of chairs for watching the Seasonal Parades in the Park - The Living Room has lots of room for entertaining, views to the neighborhood and local hills - The Dining Room comes with a beautiful built-in hutch - The Family Room is oversized and has a Wet Bar area,  a lovely Fireplace, room for a secondary eating area, and large slider to the wonderful patio - The Kitchen has loads of cabinets and Quartz counter top with  space for plenty of uses - The Main Suite is quite roomy and has a large walk-in closet with mirrored doors - This closet has loads of storage and hanging space for all your fashions - The attached bath has additional storage, dual sinks with plenty of counter area, and the shower - The Second Bedroom is quite large and has a double closet plus another one for loads of clothing and storage - The Guest Bath has a large EZ step into shower and access from the Guest bedroom - It is also available for Guests to use without the need to enter through the Bedroom - The Laundry Room is very roomy and has built-in cabinets, a Desk area with loads of space, the washer and dryer, which are included, and a door to the deep covered carport - The carport is roomy enough for up to 3 vehicles -The huge shed is massive, with two entry points with deadbolts, and power to use it as a workshop .** -  Enjoy the cool afternoon breeze while others are walking their pets around the Park or driving by in their golf carts. Stroll the Scenic greenbelts and winding walkways throughout the Park which lead to the Sparkling Lake with Fishing and Clubhouse nearby - Enjoy your Leisurely Lake Park Lifestyle! Fun includes: Parties in the Recreation Pavilion, Bingo, Bunco, Fishing, Library, Billiards, Exercise Room with newer equipment - Dinner Events - Potlucks, Casino Outings, Pool & Spa, Tennis, Pickle-ball, and more!

column79: THIS HOME IS A MUST SEE! This BEAUTIFUL HOME is located in the highly desirable Corsican Villas in Brea! You are welcomed at the entry into the spacious living room which has plenty of room to entertain and features a vaulted ceiling, and cozy electric fireplace. The dining room features recessed lighting, cabinetry for storage and is open to both the kitchen and living room. The beautiful kitchen features plenty of countertop space, stainless steel appliances, oversized sink, recessed lighting with ceiling fan, and direct access to the beautiful patio area. The Primary Suite features a large bedroom area that includes a vaulted ceiling and direct access to the patio, the bathroom includes a large sink vanity and glass enclosed shower. Down the hall is the second bedroom with a large window for natural lighting, recessed lighting and plenty of closet room. Beautiful, full bathroom with tub/shower combo just down the hall. Located within walking distance to Sonora High School, close to Downtown Brea, Brea Mall, entertainment, shopping, and restaurants. Come see this home and make it yours today!

THIS IS IT ... THE HOME YOU HAVE BEEN WAITING FOR! The most beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home you will ever see, can be yours. From the welcoming front porch, throughout the fully upgraded home, to your very own, private, serene back patio. Lots of privacy is offered on this corner lot, with only 1 home beside you. You will LOVE IT ALL! As you enter your home you will be mesmerized by it's beauty. This home offers a very open & spacious floorplan with vaulted ceilings, a walk-in pantry, shiplap covered walls & a fireplace to keep you cozy. The kitchen is gorgeous, with top of the line appliances & an oversized island you can sit around, making lots of new memories with family & friends. As you are sitting around your kitchen island, enjoy listening to music from the speaker within your refrigerator & looking at scrolling pictures on the refrigerator's display. This home is also equipped with mini split air conditioning units, which allow you to cut down on utility bills, cooling only the area of the home you are in. Crestmont is a beautiful all age community you will be so happy to call home. GET THIS ONE BEFORE IT'S GONE!

Significant Price Improvement !!! This hard to find delightful townhouse with 2BR + OFFICE or 3rd bedroom, 2.5BA in a gated community brings you HOME to a quiet location and amazingly easy, daily living. Immaculate Home. Enjoy the open, spacious floor plan on first floor with nice kitchen + dining room. New carpet throughout. All BR upstairs with 1 bathroom located in 1st floor for guests' easy accessibility. Primary BR has large en-suite, dual sinks + walk-in closet. 2nd BR and the office/bonus room have separate but immediate access to the outdoors for those clear, blue and sunny California skies in your own private veranda. Separate laundry room, washer/dryer included + 2 car attached garage. Enjoy a private, enclosed front patio and area gardening. Excellently located close to schools, shopping (Brea Mall), cluster of excellent restaurants, parks, arts + entertainment venues (Knott's Berry Farm is 3.5mi away, 5mi to Cal State Fullerton,  5.5 mi to Disneyland and a mere 25mi to Manhattan Beach). Sellers are motivated. A can't miss, must see property!

Rarely on the market, an energy efficient Pardee home with solar panels in Amerige Heights! This wonderful home is steps from the neighborhood park and just waiting for it's new family. Nice landscaping, a balcony, and an outdoor enclosed patio are the first things you will notice. As you step in, you'll find high ceilings and a very open and bright formal living and dining room. The living room is spacious enough to host a baby grand piano and lots of windows for light. The dining area has French doors that open to a peaceful faux fountain and plenty of room to host large family gatherings. The expansive kitchen opens to the family room and has its own very ample eating area. A huge, granite center island provides counter space galore and with a walk in pantry and with all the cabinets in the kitchen you will have room for all your needs. A 2 year old whole house water filtration system not only brings sparkling water but also prevents calcium build up to keep the pipes clean.  The family room has a lovely fireplace and offers lots of seating that looks out over the yard through the big windows. The eating area can support a table for at least 6. Another set of French doors will take you to a comfy porch. Finishing off the first floor is the guest bath and a fantastic ensuite bedroom with a walk in closet and a full bathroom with tub and shower. Stepping out back you find a Hobbit house offering great fun for the kids, a patio area and multiple fruit tree including Jujube, lemon, apple, and 2 kinds of persimmon trees. As you head upstairs you'll find a generously sized loft, the primary bedroom, a hall bedroom and bathroom, laundry room and another ensuite bedroom! The primary bedroom is amazing with its own fireplace, his n hers closets and sinks, a vanity, and separate shower and tub. The first room down the hall sits across from its bathroom with dual sinks and a walk in shower. The laundry room with sink and lots of cabinet space also has the linen closet just out side and finally another ensuite bedroom with a walk in closet, full bath and balcony finish off the second floor. Ceiling fans, recessed lighting, wood look tile floors, tankless water heater, dual AC units, shutters and a 3 car tandem garage add even more delight! This magnificent home is within walking distance to the top schools and all the amenities the HOA has to offer. You'll find everything you need at 1843 Catlin St in Fullerton!

Fully renovated, solar powered, pool home in the heart of Fullerton! Dual pane windows, new cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, designer tile and finishes. This home has been painted inside and out and the pool is in mint condition, ready for summer fun! Tons of outdoor area to entertain with firepit platform and dining area around the pool. Solar panels allow for generous use of central AC, heat and pool heater as needed. Primary bedroom offers ensuite with direct pool access. 4th bedroom is currently being used as an open office, but can easily be closed off to create an additional bedroom if needed. Oversized two car garage has a separate laundry area and wide driveway allows for 2 additional parking spaces. The front courtyard is perfect for a swing set and/or doggy play area. Come see all that this move in ready home has to offer before it's gone!

Welcome to the Highly desired, Family Friendly Community, "Standard Pacific Homes at Amerige Heights community". Built in 2015. (Plan 2).  4 Bedrooms plus Office/den & 4 Bathrooms, Modern tri-level layout with Open and bright floor plan, Master suite w/ Walk-in closet, Master Bathroom w/ Dual sink, Separate shower stall and bath tub, Spacious living room with a balcony by the dining area, White cabinetry, Quartz counter tops and Whirlpool stainless steel appliances in kitchen, First floor guest or In-law suite with kitchenette & full bath and direct access to the backyard and side yard, Separate laundry room on upper level, Engineer wood flooring & Recessed lighting throughout, Tank-less Water Heater & Water softening system in the garage, Extra Large Backyard that seller paid over $50,000 premium. Pre-wired and ready for cable/internet (paid for by HOA), HOA Amenities include Community Parks w/picnic area and Walking trails, Club house, 3 Tennis courts, BBQ area and much more.  Ready for move-in!

This exquisite condominium, boasting a two-car garage, is perched in the hills of Fullerton's prestigious "Westside" complex, a gem within the neighborhood. Across from the vast 105-acre Ralph B. Clark Regional Park, it is shrouded by mature trees and exudes a peaceful aura. The community is quiet, offering a soothing ambiance. Situated at the southernmost part of the complex, the residence holds a coveted spot. Its two-story corner unit guarantees seclusion, with no adjacent neighbors above or below. The unit features three upstairs bedrooms, each with custom closets. An inviting living room and a tastefully renovated kitchen with granite countertops, modern cabinets, and an informal dining nook define the space. The home includes convenient laundry facilities located in the downstairs bathroom, upgraded bathrooms, and plentiful windows that bathe the interior in natural light, enhancing its open and welcoming feel. Additional amenities include a detached two-car garage, generous guest parking, enclosed front patio perfect for pets, gardening, or barbecues. The community features include 2 pools, 1 spa, 1 children's pool, playground, and park, with the HOA managing water, trash, sewage, and common area maintenance.
Input for comp purposes only

Gorgeous family residence offering outstanding home in Fullerton Perched in the hills of Fullerton, the cul-de-sac street ends at an entrance to the famous Fullerton Loop trail system and also has easy access to all of the arts, dining, and entertainment that Fullerton is so well known. Remodeled kitchen Bathroom with quartz counter tops, and Dual pane windows, 2-zone central heat & Air Condition, ceiling fans, and a beautifully landscaped and private back yard. including Solar system. A slice of paradise!  Tranquil, inviting home ready for you.  From the traditional front porch to the amazing party patio and fruit trees in back, this home has been lovingly cared for almost 70 years by one family.  The main house consists of 1099sqft with three spacious bedrooms, a bathroom, living room, and a large kitchen with space for storage and dining.  Behind the home is a detached garage (could be an ADU?) that already has a bedroom/bath and separate room for laundry/kitchenette.  This additional space is perfect for extended family/guests or a potential rental. The yard is a treat all by itself. Giant barn-size storage shed plus smaller shed for tools or lawn care. Always wanted a she-shed?  This one is installed and ready for your ideas. This storage space is complimented by a covered concrete patio and additional lawn space, perfect for family gatherings, hosting, and so much more! With beautiful landscaping and fruit trees, this space has been enhanced for inviting indoor/outdoor living space.

Welcome to Palm Gardens, a charming community offering a low-maintenance lifestyle! This delightful 928 square foot home boasts 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and a spacious courtyard, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Step inside and discover a haven of comfort. The inviting family room features luxurious vinyl flooring for easy maintenance, while crown molding adds a touch of elegance. Double-paned vinyl windows ensure energy efficiency and a peaceful environment. A bright and airy entryway with a single door featuring glass panes welcomes you into the light-filled interior.  The functional kitchen is well-equipped for all your culinary needs. A ceiling fan keeps you cool while cooking, and a garden window adds a touch of charm. A convenient slider door opens onto the private courtyard, perfect for indoor-outdoor entertaining. For added convenience, there is a downstairs powder room. The stylish stairway leading to the bedrooms features luxury vinyl plank flooring for a modern touch. Retreat to your private haven in the spacious primary bedroom. Mirrored wardrobe closet doors maximize space, while a pocket door leading to the en-suite bathroom with a newly remodeled shower ensures privacy. The second bedroom offers versatility - use it as a guest room, home office, or hobby space. Built-in bookshelves provide ample storage, and mirrored wardrobe closet doors create a sense of spaciousness. Unwind and relax in your own private courtyard oasis. Lush greenery, including beautiful roses and bougainvillea, creates a tranquil atmosphere. Enjoy outdoor dining under the shade of the vinyl patio cover, and unwind with friends and family while surrounded by the beauty of nature. Vinyl fencing ensures privacy and a low-maintenance exterior. This move-in-ready home boasts newer plumbing and a newer heating and air conditioning system for optimal comfort. Enjoy fresh paint throughout the interior, creating a bright and inviting ambiance. The spacious two-car garage offers ample storage space for your vehicles and belongings. Laundry hookups are conveniently located inside, and vinyl plank flooring ensures easy cleaning. Built-in cabinetry provides additional storage solutions. Enjoy the benefits of a lower hoa which covers exterior maintenance and a swimming pool. This charming Palm Gardens home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and a low-maintenance lifestyle. Don't miss your opportunity to call this your own.

Turn key, completely remodeled SINGLE Story w/RV Access in the Heart of Placentia and short distances to some of the best schools in North OC: Brookhaven Elementary, Tuffree Middle, and El Dorado High schools.  If you want turn key, this is IT!  With 4 generously sized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms this home has designer touches throughout!  Remodeled Kitchen with all the things: Stainless Steel Kitchen Aid appliances, beautiful neutral grey cabinetry with brushed nickel hardware, Light colored Quartz countertops for that CLEAN modern look. BRAND NEW interior two tone paint, tiled plank flooring, recessed lighting, and updated and contemporary ceiling fans in EACH bedroom! Moving on to the master suite at rear of home includes a generously sized walk in closet and private bathroom which also has been completely remodeled in the latest trends! Plenty of room for your RV all while still having plenty of driveway space for parking!   This 4 Bedroom SINGLE story floorplan has it all: Excellent schools (most within walking distance), awesome neighborhood eateries, parks and entertainment, as well as the truly unmatched upgrades!

Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, this single-story home offers beautiful curb appeal with drought-resistant landscaping. The spacious open floor plan is designed for entertaining with plenty of natural light streaming through large windows. The extra-large living room is ideal for gatherings, featuring an attached dining area that can comfortably seat 10 or more guests.   The open kitchen boasts ample counter space, numerous cabinets, a double oven, and a spacious pantry. Perfect for entertaining, the kitchen opens into a large family room with access to the backyard. The master suite is a light-filled retreat, with sliding glass doors leading to the backyard, an attached bathroom with abundant counter space, a private shower area, and plentiful closet space with mirrored doors.  The three additional bedrooms are spacious, equipped with ceiling fans and generous closets. There is a full bathroom for the guest rooms and a powder room convenient to both the living and family rooms. The backyard is an entertainer's dream, featuring a covered patio, built-in seating area, and easy-to-maintain landscaping.  Additional highlights include beautiful laminate floors throughout, dual-pane windows, shutters, and electric blinds. The home is conveniently located within walking distance to stores, schools, and parks. This property is a perfect blend of comfort and elegance, ready for you to call home.

This quaint and cozy home has 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms at 1200 sq. ft. (approx.). The entry into the home is from a front porch that has trex decking. Once inside you are greeted with a large living room that opens to the kitchen and dining area. The kitchen has Corian countertops, plenty of cabinets and drawers, and the appliances will be included (oven/range, dishwasher, refrigerator, and countertop microwave). The primary bedroom is spacious, with a walk-in closet, and an adjoining bathroom with a walk-in shower.   The guest bedroom is nicely sized with the guest bathroom just steps away has a shower/tub combo.  Additional home features: a flex room that can be used as an office, study, or craft room, plantation shutters and flooring throughout, double-pane windows, laundry area with a full-size washer and dryer, and overhead cabinets, central a/c, and heating, a shed, and a large carport.

This beautiful mid-century home is a must see! Located on a cul-de-sac street with fresh landscaping in front and back enhancing the curb appeal, this multi-level home perfect for entertaining features 4 bedrooms, and 3 bathrooms, upon entry features original Terrazzo tile floor, vaulted and beamed ceilings, a large family room that opens to the kitchen and dining, and a second living room with a bar, and abundant natural lighting. Large backyard with plenty of room for a pool.  All bedrooms are featured upstairs and feature large windows, neutral color tones, and ample space. The charm of the home is featured on the main level with the stone full wall fireplace, warm engineered white oak flooring, and a seamless transition to the kitchen. The kitchen features abundant storage and counter space, quartz countertops, brand new appliances, a New 200 amp electrical meter perfectly prepared for solar or EV charging station, and patio access.
